g.text: South Africa released an estimated 522 MtCO2e in 2023 (excl. LULUCF), a change of -2 % compared to the previous year. Per
capita GHG emissions were 8.3 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 26.8 GtCO2, or about 1% of global
emissions to date. ⌂ EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021 ⌂ CC-BY William F. Lamb
